01:27:44,320 --> 01:27:47,280
And I wanted to see what's happening in the parts of the world

1544
01:27:47,280 --> 01:27:51,200
that I think to some extent we might fear are exploding.

1545
01:27:52,160 --> 01:27:55,760
And you have the same fundamental story

1546
01:27:55,760 --> 01:27:58,480
happening everywhere, even Nigeria.

1547
01:28:00,480 --> 01:28:03,680
So Nigeria is a good example of a country

1548
01:28:03,680 --> 01:28:08,640
